snippet.title: Prison Miners - Teaser
snippet.description:
You are condemned to darkness in the vast deserts. To survive, you must dig deeper every day with your team, improve your skills, and acquire powerful equipment. But remember… this mine is not just full of stones and ores. Stay alert to the dangers that await you. Dig, get stronger, and survive!

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3553540/Prison_Miners/
Follow Us On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/publisher/slugshotgames/
